size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2560\" data-rawheight=\"1400\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"2560\" data-original=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpicx.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-78e46a32ba251f962f7ec803e40264e2_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\" data-actualsrc=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpicx.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-78e46a32ba251f962f7ec803e40264e2_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\"\u003E\u003C\u002Ffigure\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp data-pid=\"8ikfOvXD\"\u003E接下来就是渲染部分了，设置渲染尺寸和色彩空间这些都不说哈：\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cfigure data-size=\"normal\"\u003E\u003Cnoscript\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpic3.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-2ffed8c72b17a07150fa23ec59ccbf19_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2560\" data-rawheight=\"1400\" data-qrcode-action=\"none\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2560\" data-original=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpicx.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-2ffed8c72b17a07150fa23ec59ccbf19_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\"\u003E\u003C\u002Fnoscript\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"data:image\u002Fsvg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http:\u002F\u002Fwww.w3.org\u002F2000\u002Fsvg'%20width='2560'%20height='1400'&gt;&lt;\u002Fsvg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2560\" data-rawheight=\"1400\" data-qrcode-action=\"none\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"2560\" data-original=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpicx.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-2ffed8c72b17a07150fa23ec59ccbf19_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\" data-actualsrc=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpic3.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-2ffed8c72b17a07150fa23ec59ccbf19_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\"\u003E\u003C\u002Ffigure\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp data-pid=\"1gzgn6kL\"\u003E新建摄像机固定视角：\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cfigure data-size=\"normal\"\u003E\u003Cnoscript\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpic1.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-f3dc0c87f96d1a016d95f79a4b1dceaa_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2560\" data-rawheight=\"1400\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2560\" data-original=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpic1.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-f3dc0c87f96d1a016d95f79a4b1dceaa_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\"\u003E\u003C\u002Fnoscript\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"data:image\u002Fsvg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http:\u002F\u002Fwww.w3.org\u002F2000\u002Fsvg'%20width='2560'%20height='1400'&gt;&lt;\u002Fsvg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2560\" data-rawheight=\"1400\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"2560\" data-original=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpic1.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-f3dc0c87f96d1a016d95f79a4b1dceaa_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\" data-actualsrc=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpic1.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-f3dc0c87f96d1a016d95f79a4b1dceaa_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\"\u003E\u003C\u002Ffigure\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp data-pid=\"py0emMh6\"\u003E新建环境光：\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cfigure data-size=\"normal\"\u003E\u003Cnoscript\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpicx.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-83dcffb3dff13da32a80511700924037_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2560\" data-rawheight=\"1400\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2560\" data-original=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpic1.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-83dcffb3dff13da32a80511700924037_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\"\u003E\u003C\u002Fnoscript\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"data:image\u002Fsvg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http:\u002F\u002Fwww.w3.org\u002F2000\u002Fsvg'%20width='2560'%20height='1400'&gt;&lt;\u002Fsvg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2560\" data-rawheight=\"1400\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"2560\" data-original=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpic1.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-83dcffb3dff13da32a80511700924037_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\" data-actualsrc=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpicx.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-83dcffb3dff13da32a80511700924037_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\"\u003E\u003C\u002Ffigure\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp data-pid=\"_2pHxoUb\"\u003E材质方面这里说一下，首先用了一个ao节点：\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cfigure data-size=\"normal\"\u003E\u003Cnoscript\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpicx.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-b486b028e2314a836ae0f6395fd11511_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2560\" data-rawheight=\"1400\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2560\" data-original=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpic1.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-b486b028e2314a836ae0f6395fd11511_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\"\u003E\u003C\u002Fnoscript\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"data:image\u002Fsvg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http:\u002F\u002Fwww.w3.org\u002F2000\u002Fsvg'%20width='2560'%20height='1400'&gt;&lt;\u002Fsvg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2560\" data-rawheight=\"1400\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"2560\" data-original=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpic1.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-b486b028e2314a836ae0f6395fd11511_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\" data-actualsrc=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpicx.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-b486b028e2314a836ae0f6395fd11511_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\"\u003E\u003C\u002Ffigure\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp data-pid=\"J0gxcOz-\"\u003E再用一个渐变节点对颜色进行重映射，颜色我这里就直接模仿的原作者的颜色了：\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cfigure data-size=\"normal\"\u003E\u003Cnoscript\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpic1.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-c2a8feb3e13172a53634685a5add84f4_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2560\" data-rawheight=\"1400\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2560\" data-original=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpicx.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-c2a8feb3e13172a53634685a5add84f4_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\"\u003E\u003C\u002Fnoscript\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"data:image\u002Fsvg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http:\u002F\u002Fwww.w3.org\u002F2000\u002Fsvg'%20width='2560'%20height='1400'&gt;&lt;\u002Fsvg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2560\" data-rawheight=\"1400\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"2560\" data-original=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpicx.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-c2a8feb3e13172a53634685a5add84f4_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\" data-actualsrc=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpic1.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-c2a8feb3e13172a53634685a5add84f4_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\"\u003E\u003C\u002Ffigure\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp data-pid=\"8PI7uKpU\"\u003E材质本身是一个3S材质，把这个渐变连接给漫射和吸收节点\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cfigure data-size=\"normal\"\u003E\u003Cnoscript\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpica.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-98986294498a12c1fa5e368ff3cdb548_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2560\" data-rawheight=\"1400\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2560\" data-original=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpic1.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-98986294498a12c1fa5e368ff3cdb548_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\"\u003E\u003C\u002Fnoscript\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"data:image\u002Fsvg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http:\u002F\u002Fwww.w3.org\u002F2000\u002Fsvg'%20width='2560'%20height='1400'&gt;&lt;\u002Fsvg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2560\" data-rawheight=\"1400\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"2560\" data-original=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpic1.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-98986294498a12c1fa5e368ff3cdb548_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\" data-actualsrc=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpica.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-98986294498a12c1fa5e368ff3cdb548_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\"\u003E\u003C\u002Ffigure\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp data-pid=\"Bpb6a1Ds\"\u003E我觉得现在颜色有点暗，所以用一个颜色矫正节点将颜色提亮了一点：\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cfigure data-size=\"normal\"\u003E\u003Cnoscript\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpic2.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-5b12c1f0f620429917ba595b2ff94697_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2560\" data-rawheight=\"1400\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2560\" data-original=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpic1.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-5b12c1f0f620429917ba595b2ff94697_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\"\u003E\u003C\u002Fnoscript\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"data:image\u002Fsvg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http:\u002F\u002Fwww.w3.org\u002F2000\u002Fsvg'%20width='2560'%20height='1400'&gt;&lt;\u002Fsvg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2560\" data-rawheight=\"1400\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"2560\" data-original=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpic1.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-5b12c1f0f620429917ba595b2ff94697_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\" data-actualsrc=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpic2.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-5b12c1f0f620429917ba595b2ff94697_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\"\u003E\u003C\u002Ffigure\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp data-pid=\"1I8bESSD\"\u003E再用一个噪波节点连接渐变节点制作一个蒙板：\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cfigure data-size=\"normal\"\u003E\u003Cnoscript\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpic4.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-a795336a0b121d95c911a489d381f200_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2560\" data-rawheight=\"1400\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2560\" data-original=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpic1.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-a795336a0b121d95c911a489d381f200_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\"\u003E\u003C\u002Fnoscript\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"data:image\u002Fsvg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http:\u002F\u002Fwww.w3.org\u002F2000\u002Fsvg'%20width='2560'%20height='1400'&gt;&lt;\u002Fsvg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2560\" data-rawheight=\"1400\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"2560\" data-original=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpic1.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-a795336a0b121d95c911a489d381f200_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\" data-actualsrc=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpic4.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-a795336a0b121d95c911a489d381f200_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\"\u003E\u003C\u002Ffigure\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp data-pid=\"fhdRlqFe\"\u003E把它连接到反射的强度上：\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cfigure data-size=\"normal\"\u003E\u003Cnoscript\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpic1.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-89053f624f9aaccc885aee73b36eec5e_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2560\" data-rawheight=\"1400\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2560\" data-original=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpica.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-89053f624f9aaccc885aee73b36eec5e_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\"\u003E\u003C\u002Fnoscript\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"data:image\u002Fsvg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http:\u002F\u002Fwww.w3.org\u002F2000\u002Fsvg'%20width='2560'%20height='1400'&gt;&lt;\u002Fsvg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2560\" data-rawheight=\"1400\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"2560\" data-original=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpica.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-89053f624f9aaccc885aee73b36eec5e_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\" data-actualsrc=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpic1.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-89053f624f9aaccc885aee73b36eec5e_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\"\u003E\u003C\u002Ffigure\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp data-pid=\"gS3Rk2-H\"\u003E最后我觉得文字的时候没有倒角不好看，所以又加了一个圆角节点连接到凹凸上：\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cfigure data-size=\"normal\"\u003E\u003Cnoscript\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpic2.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-8626d8e0ffb116cb59fde6ec1806d27b_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2560\" data-rawheight=\"1400\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2560\" data-original=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpic1.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-8626d8e0ffb116cb59fde6ec1806d27b_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\"\u003E\u003C\u002Fnoscript\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"data:image\u002Fsvg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http:\u002F\u002Fwww.w3.org\u002F2000\u002Fsvg'%20width='2560'%20height='1400'&gt;&lt;\u002Fsvg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2560\" data-rawheight=\"1400\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"2560\" data-original=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpic1.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-8626d8e0ffb116cb59fde6ec1806d27b_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\" data-actualsrc=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpic2.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-8626d8e0ffb116cb59fde6ec1806d27b_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\"\u003E\u003C\u002Ffigure\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp data-pid=\"kgDyS326\"\u003E地面的材质是一个普通的反射材质：\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cfigure data-size=\"normal\"\u003E\u003Cnoscript\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpicx.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-d91aa64dfc7e974bba80b7304e10128a_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2560\" data-rawheight=\"1400\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2560\" data-original=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpica.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-d91aa64dfc7e974bba80b7304e10128a_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\"\u003E\u003C\u002Fnoscript\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"data:image\u002Fsvg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http:\u002F\u002Fwww.w3.org\u002F2000\u002Fsvg'%20width='2560'%20height='1400'&gt;&lt;\u002Fsvg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2560\" data-rawheight=\"1400\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"2560\" data-original=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpica.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-d91aa64dfc7e974bba80b7304e10128a_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\" data-actualsrc=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpicx.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-d91aa64dfc7e974bba80b7304e10128a_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\"\u003E\u003C\u002Ffigure\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cp data-pid=\"bIyl6_Lr\"\u003E然后同样是用噪波节点和渐变节点制作蒙板：\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\u003Cfigure data-size=\"normal\"\u003E\u003Cnoscript\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpica.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-5dc800a73aa6bdd96755da4a477f39a3_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2560\" data-rawheight=\"1400\" data-qrcode-action=\"none\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2560\" data-original=\"https:\u002F\u002Fpic1.zhimg.com\u002Fv2-5dc800a73aa6bdd96755da4a477f39a3_720w.jpg?source=d16d100b\"\u003E\u003C\u002Fnoscript\u003E\u003Cimg src=\"data:image\u002Fsvg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg%20xmlns='http:\u002F\u002Fwww.w3.org\u002F2000\u002Fsvg'%20width='2560'%20height='1400'&gt;&l